\pard\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw10\brsp20 \widctlpar\sa160\sl252\slmult1\qj\cf0\fs24 What is Blockchain?\par

\pard\widctlpar\sa160\sl252\slmult1\qj\b0 Blockchain is about enabling peer to peer transaction in a decentralized network. Establishing trust among unknown peers. Recording the transaction in an immutable distributed ledger.\par
Blockchain enables peer to peer transfer of digital assets without any intermediaries. It was a technology originally created to support the famous cryptocurrency, Bitcoin.\par
\par

